				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13392464/scp-5440#post-4721854</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2020 08:32:46 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Lixerf</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3824744</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Its simple, Short, and good enough idea to work.<br /> But Saying it is neutralized just because incantation provided did not worked is definitely not like Foundation.</p> <p>The bush still exists, it is still present, still rooted. Its anomaly just did not remanifested.<br /> Foundation tried the incantation, but it did not worked. Their Thaumaturgists did not found anything in the incantation. Time to bring the faith experts. Some faithful enough to try.<br /> If not even that work, a ressearch about possible direct descendants of the two girls mentioned could be next step. And make the descendants try if they are found.</p> <p>The idea is definitely good. But there are still few flaws in the overall behavior of foundation in the conclusion of the article.</p> <p>No vote for now.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
